{"tid":648864,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[你個野壞左啊]呢隻公仔好百厭","createTime":"2018-05-01T05:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T08:02:44.000Z","uid":119688,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"da59558ba0eda008c2530c0388a9b9c370d4044d","tid":648864,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"本身睇人夾公仔<br />\n隻公仔一開始平放中間<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/134720_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F134720_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bb96ea4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁當然無可能一野夾到<br />\n要慢慢夾下個頭同尾 <br />\n等佢打斜跌落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知我睇到最後埋牙果下就得手果野,佢突然反左肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/134909_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F134909_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=fbee643e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都算唔緊要 反正都係磨多幾野收工<br />\n點知我打側睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/135015_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F135015_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=59244158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻狗仔有生命 隻腳咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我睇到而家佢夾左幾十野都係無收獲 呢一刻佢仲夾緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dacf5b506ecc36b87494480645a97f8d2c3c9b","tid":648864,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee5fca39868822e473185c2745ad0d9e01c53f0","tid":648864,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9dacf5b506ecc36b87494480645a97f8d2c3c9b","tid":648864,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T05:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4189d9049842fe717c44dcf7762db6e76dc4c69","tid":648864,"uid":123961,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"當哩到facebook?"},{"pid":"1b27c649db5185890aa2067446b3fa75135c2ca2","tid":648864,"uid":175032,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4189d9049842fe717c44dcf7762db6e76dc4c69","tid":648864,"uid":123961,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"當哩到facebook?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:45:06.000Z","msg":"討論區唔比討論<br />\n有野果時又話網民瘋傳冇連登份<br />\nDllm"},{"pid":"7f6989350109259c23cc78739b52ebaa011748f3","tid":648864,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"日本嗰啲？<br />\n中左包運費？"},{"pid":"740be0f014b63fe992dbe427fb4184dcc8479158","tid":648864,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb30a2fbaf4c6d5cc6033f5c02fa654ccd64a257","tid":648864,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f6989350109259c23cc78739b52ebaa01174